snippet.title: TS!UNDERSWAP Demo - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After 4 years in development, the TS!UNDERSWAP Demo is out!
DOWNLOAD HERE: https://teamswitched.gamejolt.io/
https://gamejolt.com/p/december-2020-demo-release-before-you-play-rmfwadpe

Voiced by @Audiospawn's Sudzy Bubbles 
Trailer created by @Ethosein and NetherHeartz
3D model by CheezedFish
Extra contributions by colinator27 and AllyTally
TS!UNDERSWAP by Team Switched
UNDERTALE by Toby Fox

--

TS!UNDERSWAP is an unofficial fan-game of Toby Fox's UNDERTALE, made by Team Switched (TS). It is a re-imagining based on the premise of swapping character roles, and adding original content, to create new scenarios.

By doing so, we aim to provide a brand new experience for fans of UNDERTALE, while staying true to its aesthetic and characters.

Like the project? Make sure to follow our progress!
Website - https://teamswitched.gamejolt.io/
GameJolt - https://gamejolt.com/games/tsunderswap/160094
Discord - https://discord.gg/2URNfyk
Tumblr - https://tsunderswapofficial.tumblr.com/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/tswitched
Official Wiki - https://tsunderswapofficial.wikia.com/wiki/TS!Underswap_Wiki
